  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for 2030 agenda for sustainable development and climate change&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;This grant will support the Office of the Special Adviser on the 2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development and Climate Change to provide leadership to the UN system to implement the Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs). The Office of the Special Adviser will carry out activities that include producing public commentary and analysis on the SDGs, developing official directives from the Secretary General, establishing UN-wide strategies for SDG implementation, and coordinating necessary changes within the UN system to respond to the new SDGs. The Office of the Special Adviser will work with UN agencies, member states, and civil society to carry out these activities.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
